headline.main: Old Enmity Behind Poland's Push to Oust EU's Tusk
headline.print_headline: Old Enmity Behind Poland's Push to Oust EU's Tusk

lead_paragraph: In trying to prise former Polish prime minister Donald Tusk out of one of the European Union's top jobs, the ruling conservatives in Warsaw may have another battle in mind: the 2020 presidential election in Poland.
